    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable, no-frills daily driver. Mechanically, it starts right up and handles well, though it will likely need routine maintenance on the suspension and brakes in the near future. The exterior has several visible signs of age, including door dings, faded paint on the hood, and a small crack in the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows wear, such as some staining on the upholstery and a worn steering wheel. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that isn't a showpiece but will get you where you need to go.",
      "price": 21000.0,
